## ğŸ—„ï¸ Database Schema

### Main Tables
- `users` - Admin and member accounts
- `memberships` - Subscription records
- `payments` - Payment transactions
- `classes` - Recurring class schedules
- `class_instances` - Actual class occurrences
- `bookings` - Member class bookings
- `notifications` - System notifications
- `settings` - System configuration
- `admin_actions` - Audit log

See [schema.sql](gym-backend/database/schema.sql) for complete schema.

## ğŸ” Environment Variables

### Backend (.env)
```env
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=5000

DB_HOST=localhost
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=your_password
DB_NAME=gym_management

JWT_SECRET=your-secret-key
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your_account_sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_auth_token
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890

FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

### Frontend (.env)
```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
VITE_SOCKET_URL=http://localhost:5000
```

